{"tid":2190240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又撤控！李偲嫣兒子涉毆繼父至骨折　獲撤控簽保守行為　","createTime":"2020-09-05T13:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T13:12:18.000Z","uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"029cb643c3347c9ffbba00cbe0a75b20db533bd3","tid":2190240,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/李偲嫣兒子涉毆繼父至骨折-獲撤控簽保守行為-官曾質疑-控罪唔輕喎/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%B2%E5%AB%A3%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E6%B6%89%E6%AF%86%E7%B9%BC%E7%88%B6%E8%87%B3%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98-%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%A4%E6%8E%A7%E7%B0%BD%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E5%AE%98%E6%9B%BE%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA%E5%94%94%E8%BC%95%E5%96%8E%2F&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=7b7e13d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%B2%E5%AB%A3%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E6%B6%89%E6%AF%86%E7%B9%BC%E7%88%B6%E8%87%B3%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98-%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%A4%E6%8E%A7%E7%B0%BD%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E5%AE%98%E6%9B%BE%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA%E5%94%94%E8%BC%95%E5%96%8E%2F&h=63f6be03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/李偲嫣兒子涉毆繼父至骨折-獲撤控簽保守行為-官曾質疑-控罪唔輕喎/</a><br />\n<br />\n「正義聯盟」創黨主席李偲嫣的兒子劉仲朗，被指於今年 6 月與繼父謝鋮浚爭執，其後用三腳架毆打對方至面骨骨折，被控一項傷人罪，還押至今（4 日）在屯門裁判法院再提堂。<span class=\"red\">控方表示索取律政司意見後，同意以簽保守行為方式處理。</span>裁判官張潔宜聞言即稱：「傷勢唔輕喎」，終批准被告自簽 2,000 元、守行為 18 個月撤回控罪，以及支付 500 元堂費。<br />\n被告為李偲嫣的兒子劉仲朗（26歲，報稱廚師），原被控傷人罪，指他於今年 6 月 26 日在元朗八鄉路，非法及惡意傷害男子謝鋮浚。劉一度表示堂費在其保釋金扣除，裁判官稱：「你還押邊有保釋金？」<br />\n劉仲朗的同意案情指，李偲嫣及謝鋮浚於 2018 年結婚，被告為謝的繼子。今年 6 月 26 日凌晨 3 時多，三人到元朗食宵夜後，謝駕車回家，期間被告接聽電話後情緒激動，踢向司機椅背。謝不滿遂將車停在路旁，與被告爭執。被告拿起三腳架，毆打劉約 10 分鐘，乘搭的士離開。5 分鐘後，被告折返現場，再次用腳架毆打謝的頭及身體約 5 分鐘。謝送院治理，發現面骨骨折，面部和前臂亦有瘀傷。<br />\n案件編號：TMCC1087/2020"},{"pid":"f8ac5866596d0d712123925524fe483ecb605731","tid":2190240,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccb4bb21e19e9fe7d4d32561a0fb168eeab7b997","tid":2190240,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37c641e4c3d8eee17c0c708af2449ffb07d585d","tid":2190240,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8ec090a02207ad4e5775ee5d2027f6cf34da95d","tid":2190240,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:11:04.000Z","msg":"繼兒動武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e56c04b00ce94d1b578533b9aeba7959ace196","tid":2190240,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:12:18.000Z","msg":"推"}]}